You are a senior full-stack engineer and product designer. Build GeoAttend — a production-grade PWA SaaS for geo-tagged employee attendance management targeting Kerala-based small businesses (gold shops, jewellery traders, field sales teams). It must feel like a funded startup product, not a weekend project.

═══════════════════════════════════════════
TECH STACK
═══════════════════════════════════════════
- Next.js 15 (App Router, Server Actions)
- Tailwind CSS v4
- Material UI v6
- MongoDB Atlas via Mongoose
- NextAuth.js v5 (credentials + Google OAuth)
- Leaflet.js + React-Leaflet (maps)
- jsPDF + jspdf-autotable (PDF reports)
- next-pwa + Workbox (PWA/offline)
- Cloudinary (photo storage, free tier)
- Zustand (state management)
- React Hook Form + Zod (forms + validation)
- react-hot-toast (notifications)
- Recharts (analytics charts)
- Lucide React + MUI Icons

