═══════════════════════════════════════════
PAGE SPECIFICATIONS
═══════════════════════════════════════════

LOGIN (/login):
- Split layout: left panel = product illustration + "Trusted by Kerala's gold traders", right = form
- Fields: Email, Password. Google OAuth button
- Demo credentials shown: demo@geoattend.in / Demo@1234
- Links: Forgot password, Register

REGISTER (/register):
- 3-step form with progress indicator:
  Step 1: Business name, type (Jewellery/Gold Trading/Retail/Other), city
  Step 2: Owner name, phone (10 digits), email, password (min 8 chars + special char)
  Step 3: Team size selection, confirmation summary
- Full Zod validation on every field

OWNER DASHBOARD (/dashboard):
- Stats row (4 cards): Today Present, Today Absent, Currently Checked In, Late Arrivals
- Left 60%: Live Leaflet map with employee location pins
- Right 40%: Recent check-ins feed (avatar + name + time + status badge)
- Bottom: 14-day attendance bar chart (Recharts) + Top Performer card
- All data from real API calls with skeleton loaders

EMPLOYEES (/employees):
- Grid of employee cards: Avatar, Name, Role badge, Department, Phone, Today status badge, View button
- Top bar: Search, Role filter, Add Employee button
- Add Employee modal: Name, phone, email, role, department, joining date — all Zod validated
- Employee detail page (/employees/[id]): Profile header, attendance calendar heatmap, stats, recent log table
- Empty state: Illustrated with "Add your first team member" CTA

ATTENDANCE LOG (/attendance):
- Dense table: Employee avatar+name, Date, Check-in time+location, Check-out time, Hours, Status badge, Photo thumbnail (click expands)
- Filters: Date range picker, Employee dropdown, Status filter
- Pagination: 10 rows/page
- Export: "Export PDF" and "Export CSV" buttons
- Row colors: green=present, amber=late, red=absent

LIVE MAP (/attendance/live):
- Full-width Leaflet map, satellite/street toggle
- Custom employee markers: green=checked in, grey=not yet
- Marker popup: Name, check-in time, photo thumbnail, View Profile link
- Sidebar list of all employees with real-time status

REPORTS (/reports):
- Filter panel: Date range, employee multi-select, report type (Daily Summary / Monthly Payroll / Individual)
- Preview panel showing report structure
- Generate PDF → branded PDF download with:
  Business logo + name header, summary table (employee, days present/absent/late, total hours), individual logs with coordinates, page numbers, generated timestamp
- Monthly trend chart

SETTINGS (/settings):
- Tabs: Business Profile | Geofence | Work Hours | Notifications
- Business Profile: Name, address, logo upload, contact
- Geofence: Leaflet map with draggable radius circle, radius slider (50m–2km), address search
- Work Hours: Start/end time, grace period (minutes), working days checkboxes (Mon–Sun)
- Notifications: Toggles for late alerts, absence alerts, weekly report email

EMPLOYEE CHECK-IN (/checkin) — MOBILE FIRST:
- Step 1: Large "Check In" button, current time + date displayed
- Step 2: GPS acquisition, animated spinner, accuracy indicator in metres
- Step 3: Camera capture using browser Camera API, live viewfinder
- Step 4: Confirm screen — location address + photo preview + Submit
- Step 5: Success screen with check animation + "You're checked in!"
- Offline banner: "No internet — will sync when connected", stores to IndexedDB

EMPLOYEE HISTORY (/history):
- Mobile-optimised list of own attendance records
- Status badges, hours worked, location address per day

═══════════════════════════════════════════
API ROUTES
═══════════════════════════════════════════
POST   /api/auth/register
POST   /api/auth/[...nextauth]
GET    /api/employees                    — all employees for business
POST   /api/employees                    — create employee
GET    /api/employees/:id                — single + stats
PATCH  /api/employees/:id                — update
DELETE /api/employees/:id                — deactivate
GET    /api/attendance                   — filtered list (date, employee, status)
POST   /api/attendance                   — new check-in
PATCH  /api/attendance/:id               — add check-out or update
GET    /api/attendance/live              — today, all employees
POST   /api/upload                       — photo → Cloudinary → return URL
GET    /api/reports/pdf                  — generate + stream PDF
GET    /api/reports/stats                — dashboard aggregated stats

All routes: validate request body with Zod before DB operations. Add MongoDB indexes on businessId, employeeId, date fields.

═══════════════════════════════════════════
PWA + OFFLINE
═══════════════════════════════════════════
next.config.js: configure next-pwa with dest: 'public', register: true, skipWaiting: true
Runtime caching for: API attendance responses, Leaflet map tiles, Cloudinary employee photos

manifest.json:
{
  "name": "GeoAttend",
  "short_name": "GeoAttend",
  "theme_color": "#1B4332",
  "background_color": "#ffffff",
  "display": "standalone",
  "start_url": "/checkin",
  "icons": [72, 96, 128, 144, 152, 192, 384, 512]
}

useOfflineSync.ts:
- Store pending check-ins in IndexedDB using idb-keyval
- Listen to navigator.onLine changes
- On reconnect, flush queue to /api/attendance with exponential retry

useGeolocation.ts: wrap navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition with Promise, return { lat, lng, accuracy, error }
useCamera.ts: wrap getUserMedia({ video: { facingMode: 'environment' } }), expose capturePhoto() returning base64 JPEG

